[
    {
        "content": "<p>Hello, I am trying to reimplement a simple C out-of-tree misc device in Rust, based on the original rust branch which has the <a href=\"https://rust-for-linux.github.io/docs/rust/kernel/macro.module_misc_device.html\">misc device macro</a>. The module should register a misc device that allows a simple form of communication between two processes by reading and writing to it.</p>\n<p>My question arises from the fact that (for my understanding) a struct which implements the <a href=\"https://rust-for-linux.github.io/docs/rust/kernel/file/trait.Operations.html\"><code>kernel::file::Operations</code> trait</a> is not supposed to have shared data between multiple file handles, but only local to a single handle through the <code>Self::Data</code> type. For my use case, though, I need a shared buffer between multiple handles/threads. So what would be the most idiomatic approach to do it?</p>\n<p>Here's the C module:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"C\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"cp\">#include</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cpf\">&lt;linux/poll.h&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#include</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cpf\">&lt;linux/module.h&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#include</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cpf\">&lt;linux/moduleparam.h&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#include</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cpf\">&lt;linux/init.h&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#include</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cpf\">&lt;linux/miscdevice.h&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"cp\">#include</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"cpf\">&lt;linux/slab.h&gt;</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"n\">MODULE_AUTHOR</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"Antonio Napolitano\"</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"n\">MODULE_DESCRIPTION</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"Test for misc devices\"</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"n\">MODULE_LICENSE</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"GPL\"</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">static</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">char</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">my_pointer</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"k\">static</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">int</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">my_len</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">static</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">int</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">my_open</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">inode</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">inode</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">file</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">file</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">static</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">int</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">my_close</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">inode</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">inode</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">file</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">file</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"kt\">ssize_t</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">my_read</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">file</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">file</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">char</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">__user</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">buf</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">size_t</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">len</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">loff_t</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">ppos</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"kt\">int</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">res</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">err</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">len</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">my_len</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">res</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">my_len</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"p\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">else</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">res</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">len</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">my_pointer</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">==</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">NULL</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">err</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">copy_to_user</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">buf</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">my_pointer</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">res</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">err</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">EFAULT</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">kfree</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">my_pointer</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">my_pointer</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">NULL</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">res</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">static</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">ssize_t</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">my_write</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">file</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">file</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">const</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">char</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">__user</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">buf</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">size_t</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">count</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">loff_t</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"n\">ppos</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"kt\">int</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">err</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">my_pointer</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">-1</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">my_pointer</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kmalloc</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">count</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">GFP_USER</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">my_pointer</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">==</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">NULL</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">-1</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">my_len</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">count</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">err</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">copy_from_user</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">my_pointer</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">buf</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">count</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">if</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">err</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">EFAULT</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">count</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">static</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">file_operations</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">my_fops</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">owner</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">THIS_MODULE</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">read</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"n\">my_read</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">open</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"n\">my_open</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">release</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\">      </span><span class=\"n\">my_close</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">write</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"n\">my_write</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">};</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">static</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">miscdevice</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">test_device</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">MISC_DYNAMIC_MINOR</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"test\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"n\">my_fops</span>\n<span class=\"p\">};</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"k\">static</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">int</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">testmodule_init</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"kt\">int</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">res</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">res</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">misc_register</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"n\">test_device</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">printk</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"s\">\"Misc Register returned %d</span><span class=\"se\">\\n</span><span class=\"s\">\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">res</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"k\">return</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">0</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">static</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">testmodule_exit</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"kt\">void</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">misc_deregister</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">&amp;</span><span class=\"n\">test_device</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">module_init</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">testmodule_init</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n<span class=\"n\">module_exit</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">testmodule_exit</span><span class=\"p\">);</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>And my current Rust implementation:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\">// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">use</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"p\">::{</span><span class=\"n\">io_buffer</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">types</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ForeignOwnable</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">file</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">File</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">prelude</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">};</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">module_misc_device</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">type</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">MyMiscDev</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"test\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">author</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"Antonio Napolitano\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">description</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"Rust misc device\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">license</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"GPL\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"cp\">#[derive(Default)]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">MyMiscDev</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"cp\">#[vtable]</span>\n<span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">file</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Operations</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">MyMiscDev</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">open</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">_context</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">OpenData</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">_file</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">File</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Result</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Data</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nb\">Ok</span><span class=\"p\">(())</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">write</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">_data</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"bp\">Self</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Data</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">as</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ForeignOwnable</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Borrowed</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;'</span><span class=\"nb\">_</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">_file</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">File</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">reader</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"nc\">mut</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">io_buffer</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">IoBufferReader</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">_offset</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kt\">u64</span><span class=\"p\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nb\">Result</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"kt\">usize</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">        </span><span class=\"nb\">Ok</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">reader</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">len</span><span class=\"p\">())</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"p\">}</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
