        "content": "<p>Okay, I think I found a solution: I manually implemented the misc device from a base <code>Module</code> with a custom <code>type OpenData = Arc&lt;Pin&lt;Box&lt;Mutex&lt;Vec&lt;u8&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;</code>. Here's the complete code for future reference:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c1\">// SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0</span>\n\n<span class=\"sd\">//! Misc device module that allows communication between two processes.</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">use</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">kernel</span><span class=\"p\">::{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">file</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">File</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">file</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Operations</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">io_buffer</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">miscdev</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Registration</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">mutex_init</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">prelude</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"o\">*</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">sync</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Arc</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">sync</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">Mutex</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">types</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"n\">ForeignOwnable</span><span class=\"p\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Module</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">};</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">module</span><span class=\"o\">!</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">type</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">MyModule</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">name</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"rust_misc_dev\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">author</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"Antonio Napolitano\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">description</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"Rust misc device\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">license</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"GPL\"</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">const</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">DEV_NAME</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kp\">&amp;</span><span class=\"kt\">str</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s\">\"test\"</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">MyModule</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">MyMiscDevModule</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">MyFile</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">type</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">MyOpenData</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Arc</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Pin</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"nb\">Box</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Mutex</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"nb\">Vec</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"kt\">u8</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">struct</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">MyMiscDevModule</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Operations</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">OpenData</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">MyOpenData</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"n\">_reg</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Pin</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"nb\">Box</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">Registration</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n<span class=\"p\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"k\">impl</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">Operations</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">OpenData</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">MyOpenData</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Module</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">MyMiscDevModule</span><span class=\"o\">&lt;</span><span class=\"n\">T</span><span class=\"o\">&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">{</span>\n<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"k\">fn</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nf\">init</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">_name</span><span class=\"p\">:</s